OL,7,FHearldon joined the firm in May 2014.
OL,8,F"By all accounts he was viewed as a
OL,9,Fpopular and diligent member of the
OL,10,Faccounting department," he said.
OL,12,FThe court heard that by August 2021 he
OL,13,Fhad been promoted to the role of
OL,14,Fsenior managing clerk, a position
OL,15,Fwhich involved him in 'all areas of
OL,16,Fthe company's financial affairs'.
