OL,6,FMr Donnelly said the firm's turnover
OL,7,Fwas 'running into the tens of millions
OL,8,Fof pounds annually', adding that a
OL,9,F'small part' of the company's business
OL,10,Fwas conducted via the PayPal payment
OL,11,Fsystem.
OL,13,FAn audit of the company's finances was
OL,14,Fcarried out in 2021 which raised
OL,15,F'concerns' about a 'discrepancy'.
OL,17,FHearldon initially tried to 'explain
OL,18,Fit away' when questioned, but after he
OL,19,Fwas confronted again by company bosses
OL,20,Fhe confessed.
