OL,6,FIt was discovered that Hearldon had
OL,7,Fmade 140 transactions over a near
OL,8,Fthree year period.
OL,10,F"It seems that the company's PayPal
OL,11,Faccount was being used as a personal
OL,12,Faccount by Mr Hearldon to extract sums
OL,13,Fof money which were not
OL,14,Finsubstantial," Mr Donnelly said.
OL,16,FHe was 'summarily dismissed', and
OL,17,Fattended a voluntary interview with
OL,18,Fpolice.
