OL,7,Fdebt and that he had started to steal
OL,8,F'small amounts' but had then 'lost
OL,9,Fcontrol'.
OL,11,FHe has since paid back #43,000 of the
OL,12,Fmoney stolen. Mr Donnelly said that it
OL,13,Fwas discovered that Hearldon had
OL,14,Fpurchased a Range Rover and a 'holiday
OL,15,Fhome' in .
